@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kvzesp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.95 + tmp + 0.46)) / wp.cos(0.10))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.80) - (v1 + 0.61 + v0 + 0.25)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.81)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) - 0.36)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.91) * (v1 + 0.24 / v0 + 0.19)))
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = (v1 - wp.abs(0.74))
    data[tid] = v0
